## 10. Overall Judgment

After reviewing the stack, try to answer these directly:

- [ ] The valuation framework is economically coherent end to end.
- [ ] The most important current weaknesses are now explicit in the docs.
- [ ] I know which 3 to 5 follow-on issues matter most.
- [ ] I can tell what should be deterministic, what should be LLM-augmented, and what should remain PM judgment.
- [ ] I would be comfortable using this doc set as the canon for future valuation hardening.

